      "summary": {
        "zh": "动量策略在弱势市场中持续发出持有信号，等待确认以避免过早入场。低RSI和混合MACD信号暗示弱势，但有限的近期跌幅和中性偏正面的新闻支持耐心等待。低胜率（约37-38%）和中等回撤（15-21%）是长期收益的主要侵蚀因素，需通过风险管理来缓解。",
        "en": "Momentum strategy consistently issues hold signals in weak markets, waiting for confirmation to avoid premature entry. Low RSI and mixed MACD signals indicate weakness, but limited recent declines and neutral-to-positive news support patience. Low win rates (~37-38%) and moderate drawdowns (15-21%) are key eroders of long-term returns, requiring risk management to mitigate."
      },
      "key_findings": [
